SWISS DAYBOOK: OC Oerlikon, UBS, Roche, Holcim, Emmi Earnings

-- B y   E l e n a   L o g u t e n k o v a
-- 
2011-08-31T05:44:38Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-08-31/swiss-daybook-oc-oerlikon-ubs-roche-holcim-emmi-earnings.html
OC Oerlikon Corp. Chief Executive
Officer Michael Buscher said a merger with  Sulzer AG (SUN)  isn’t a
topic for the company, Finanz und Wirtschaft reported.  EQUITIES:
*SGS acquires Environmental Testing Corporation
*Roche’s repacked Avastin found linked to cluster of eye
infections, FDA says
*UBS cut three jobs in its Canadian financial-adviser network
*Holcim raised to “buy” at Jefferies
*Emmi said first-half sales increased
*Feintool changes its business year  ECONOMY:
*Switzerland’s government holds regular meeting
* Swiss National Bank  publishes July currency holdings  MARKETS:
*The SMI rose 0.1 percent to 5,449.16.
*The SPI increased 0.2 percent to 4,971.48.
*The Stoxx Europe 600 Index rose 1 percent to 230.64.
*The MSCI Asia-Pacific Index gained 0.9 percent at 7:42 a.m.
Zurich time
